data.description: Location, Location, Location ! Welcome to this charming home !! Great opportunity to own a well-maintained 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom Single Family Home in the community of Montego Bay in Kissimmee. ROOF REPLACED MAY 2022. NEW A/C 2023. NEW EXTERIOR PAINT. Stainless Steel appliances (2 years old). Laminate flooring. 2 car garage. Low HOA. Close to Disney, SeaWorld, Universal Studios, shopping malls, restaurants, and much more. Montego Bay is a desirable community with pool, playground, tennis and basketball courts. GREAT LOCATION in Kissimmee area. This home is also ZONED FOR SHORT TERM RENTALS. If you are looking for a primary residence or investment property, this is the home. Call to schedule a private showing !!
